ows up half way up on the mana bar.<br>- Removed all % signs next to figures. Once you understand that they are percentage values, you don't need a label to tell you that. Every element, every figure, should tell you something useful, not something you already know.<br>- The whole window size was reduced by 5 pixils on the left and bottom. It doesn't sound like a lot but this is over 3000 pixils overall saved.<br><br><br>Here's a screenshot:<br><br><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://loralciriclight.com/images/advanced_group_window.jpg"><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br><br>Overall the window should now support melees, casters, pet casters, healers and hybrids all equally well.  Please let me know how it works out for you.<br><br>A download of the mod and installation instructions can be found at <br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://loralciriclight.com/ui.html">loralciriclight.com/ui.html</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br>Thanks!<br> <p><a href="http://loralciriclight.com/"><img src="http://loralciriclight.com/images/loral_dragon_sig.jpg" border="0" alt="Loral's Signature" height="132" width="302"></a><br /><a href="http://loralciriclight.com/loral.html">bio</a> - <a href="http://loralciriclight.com/">stories</a> - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=16545">equip</a> - <a href="http://loralciriclight.com/images/">screenshots</a> - <a href="http://loralciriclight.com/refdesk.html">eq links</a></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uloral.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Loral</A> at: 8/11/02 8:56:13 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucharnaslightbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Charnas Lightbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Charnas > Samadhi</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/11/02 9:39:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm41.showAddR